  "steps": [
    {
      "order": 1,
      "instruction": "Combine Spice Mix in a shallow dish and mix."
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Coat both sides of the fish fillets with the Spice Mix, shaking off excess."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Heat oil in a large heavy based skillet over medium high heat."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Add fish and cook until the rub turns black, then flip and cook the other side until the fish is cooked to your taste. (Note 2)"
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "instruction": "Serve immediately. I served mine with a buttery Corn Rice Salad - refer to the Notes for the recipe."
